002c_5th_generation_U002c_4th_generation_U002c_3rd_generation_U0029_2048_x_2732_pixels___U0028portrait_U0029-4.png/576x768bb.png","https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource211/v4/84/71/a8/8471a80c-a774-b0f5-a57e-a2d8fca80efa/5dafb38e-4250-41bd-8c95-f2f95038dc3c_lay__iPad_Pro__U00286th_generation_U002c_5th_generation_U002c_4th_generation_U002c_3rd_generation_U0029_2048_x_2732_pixels___U0028portrait_U0029-5.png/576x768bb.png","https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource211/v4/b5/06/86/b5068686-f13c-102c-b3fc-d9e35f3adca0/ce9da859-09e1-48c5-b88f-4c69d77494bc_lay__iPad_Pro__U00286th_generation_U002c_5th_generation_U002c_4th_generation_U002c_3rd_generation_U0029_2048_x_2732_pixels___U0028portrait_U0029-6.png/576x768bb.png","https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource221/v4/7d/cf/69/7dcf69cd-b19c-a5fa-a6b3-2968b8a242b9/90095790-926a-4208-8d21-334976d77da7_lay__iPad_Pro__U00286th_generation_U002c_5th_generation_U002c_4th_generation_U002c_3rd_generation_U0029_2048_x_2732_pixels___U0028portrait_U0029-7.png/576x768bb.png"],"appletvScreenshotUrls":[],"artworkUrl512":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/87/bd/e7/87bde7ce-4d0e-3093-621e-9086d423aa17/AppIcon-Final-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","minimumOsVersion":"17.0","trackCensoredName":"Vivaldi Powerful Web Browser","trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/vivaldi-powerful-web-browser/id1633234600?uo=4","contentAdvisoryRating":"17+","averageUserRating":4.84673,"artistId":1633234602,"artistName":"Vivaldi Technologies","bundleId":"com.vivaldi.browser","primaryGenreName":"Utilities","primaryGenreId":6002,"releaseDate":"2023-09-27T07:00:00Z","trackId":1633234600,"trackName":"Vivaldi Powerful Web Browser","isVppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"currentVersionReleaseDate":"2026-04-09T14:10:49Z","releaseNotes":"Vivaldi 7.9 is a big one. We're adding a signature Vivaldi feature arrives on iOS! \n\nWhats's new with this release:\n\n- Tab Stacks on iOS: Group your tabs into stacks and see them on two levels. This signature Vivaldi feature improves tab management significally! Long-press the New Tab button to create a new stack, and choose between Two-Level or Accordion style in Settings.\n\n- Daily Background Image: A new photograph on your Start Page every day, allowing you to send your thoughts of to a different location every day. \n\n- Import from Safari:  Bring your bookmarks, passwords, history, and more into Vivaldi in seconds. You've spent long enough being a safari attraction. Time to be the explorer, of the web.\n\n\nYour browser, your rules.\n\nLove Vivaldi? Give us a 5-star rating and share it with friends who deserve a better browser!","version":"7.9.3980.91","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"Vivaldi Browser is a powerful, personal, and private web browser. It comes packed with built-in features including desktop-style tabs, an Ad Blocker, tracking protection. Designed to put you back in control. Trusted by millions of users across the world.\n\nFEATURES:\n- Ad Blocker: Browse with minimal distractions.\n- Tracker Blocker: Stay protected with leading privacy and security features.\n- Custom Wallpapers & Themes: Pick a theme and background that matches your style.\n- Dark Mode for all webpages: Force Dark Mode to every website you visit.\n- Desktop-like tabs: Efficiently manage multiple websites at once.\n- Encrypted Sync: Seamlessly sync data across your mobile and desktop devices.\n- Notes: Jot down thoughts and ideas while browsing.\n- Bookmarks: Organize your favorite sites effortlessly.\n- Reading Lists: Save articles for offline reading.\n- Custom App Icon: Personalize Vivaldi's appearance on your home screen.\n- Switch Search Engines: Choose your preferred search engine on the fly.\n\nPOWERFUL\nPacked with flexible features, all built in.\n\nPERSONAL\nYou make it your own, Vivaldi adapts to you.\n\nPRIVATE\nWe don't track you, or your behavior.\n\nDESKTOP-LIKE TABS\nBring the robust tab management from your desktop to your iOS device. Vivaldi on iOS features a unique Tab Bar akin to the desktop browser. To activate or deactivate the Tab Bar, head to Vivaldi menu > Settings, and tap on \"Show Tab Bar\" to toggle the setting.\n\nSYNC ACROSS DEVICES\nNever feel out of touch. Sync your data across devices with end-to-end encryption. From open tabs and saved logins to bookmarks and notes, everything is seamlessly available wherever you go. Add an extra layer of security with an encryption password.\n\nSET AS DEFAULT BROWSER\nReady to make the switch? Set Vivaldi as your default browser and experience the web like never before. Here's how: Go to Settings, scroll down to Vivaldi, and select it as your Default Browser App. It's that simple!\n\nABOUT VIVALDI\nWith millions active users and a vibrant community of over 1.4 million members worldwide, Vivaldi is redefining what a web browser can be. At Vivaldi, we believe a browser should be powerful, personal, and private. With our unique philosophy of \"respect, question, create, and deliver,\" we're crafting a browsing experience that adapts to you, not the other way around.\n\nSome of the links in this app are affiliate links. If you make a purchase through these links, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps support the development of Vivaldi and keeps the web browser independent. Thank you for your support!\n\nBy downloading Vivaldi, you are agreeing to the End User License Agreement at https://vivaldi.com/privacy/vivaldi-end-user-license-agreement/. Learn more about how Vivaldi handles and protects your data in our Privacy Policy at https://vivaldi.com/privacy/browser/.","languageCodesISO2A":["AF","BE","BG","CA","CS","DA","NL","EN","ET","FI","FR","KA","DE","EL","HU","IS","ID","IT","JA","KO","NB","PL","PT","RU","SR","ZH","SK","SL","ES","SV","ZH","TR","UK"],"fileSizeBytes":"237112320","formattedPrice":"Free","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":1044,"trackContentRating":"17+","sellerUrl":"https://vivaldi.com/ios/","averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.84673,"sellerName":"Vivaldi Technologies AS","genreIds":["6002","6007"],"genres":["Utilities","Productivity"],"price":0.0,"userRatingCount":1044}